        <p>A little about myself and the project.</p>
        <p> I'm Shane, I've been working on this board game in my free time for a few years.</p>
        <p>In the last few months I've begun to take it more seriously and am ready to order prototypes. My current goal is to do an initial release on a crowdfunding website in April.</p>
